        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780900860867" href="/book/show/640460.Assemblies_of_Al_Hariri">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer859324825" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14119507996497089176">Despite the fact that this is a translation from Arabic, it is an outstanding, luscious, eloquent, example of demonstration via dialogue. A sadly neglected work. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


