          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9781479800841" href="/book/show/48815915-impostures">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/8101737-peter-tillman?shelf=fantasy">fantasy</a>, 
